What...

44
00:03:41,400 --> 00:03:42,480
What does this have to do
with Xu Jingyang?

45
00:03:42,510 --> 00:03:42,840
I...

46
00:03:44,680 --> 00:03:45,030
Xiaoyuan,

47
00:03:45,800 --> 00:03:46,280
I'm sorry.

48
00:03:46,960 --> 00:03:48,360
You got involved because of me.

49
00:03:50,310 --> 00:03:51,840
What do you mean?

50
00:03:53,710 --> 00:03:54,150
You know how space travel happened,

51
