144
00:09:31,950 --> 00:09:33,120
- Sure.
- Great.

145
00:09:33,630 --> 00:09:34,630
- Thank you, Xiaoyuan.
- Thanks, Xiaoyuan.

146
00:09:34,680 --> 00:09:35,720
Thank you all.

147
00:09:40,510 --> 00:09:41,160
Xiaoyuan,

148
00:09:42,000 --> 00:09:43,680
I formally invite you

149
00:09:44,070 --> 00:09:44,800
to be the regular makeup artist

150
00:09:44,920 --> 00:09:45,800
for our theater group.

151
00:09:47,120 --> 00:09:48,360
Thanks for the kind offer, Mr. Cui.

152
00:09:49,000 --> 00:09:50,160
But my company has stopped

153
00:09:50,310 --> 00:09:51,390
the makeup services.

154
00:09:51,830 --> 00:09:53,070
So I might not be able

155
00:09:53,070 --> 00:09:53,920
to continue with makeup.

156
00:09:54,480 --> 00:09:55,830
You're not doing makeup anymore?

157
00:09:56,480 --> 00:09:57,720
But you are amazing.

158
00:09:57,720 --> 00:09:58,720
Couldn't you convince your company

159
00:09:58,830 --> 00:09:59,830
to keep this service?

160
00:10:00,070 --> 00:10:01,360
I'd say, why not consider
a job change?

161
00:10:01,950 --> 00:10:02,920
With Xiaoyuan's skills,

162
00:10:03,000 --> 00:10:03,800
